    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your eyes briefly become pools of darkness, and ghostly, flightless wings sprout from your back temporarily. Creatures of your choice within 10 feet of you that can see you must succeed on a Charisma saving throw (DC 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma modifier; chosen when you select this species) or become frightened of you until the end of your next turn. Until the transformation ends, once on each of your turns, you can deal extra necrotic damage to one target when you deal damage to it. The extra damage equals your proficiency bonus.</p><section id=\"secret-3SdS5UyDWZQZoZHI\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>When you select this species, you will need to choose Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma for the saving throw for this feature and apply it in the Details section. Under \"Feature Attack\" set the Ability Modifier to the chosen ability.</p></section>",
